{"tid":1535673,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"由耶撚角度睇成場運動","createTime":"2019-09-03T12:33:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T14:15:42.000Z","uid":260292,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"6dd640ee20bcc280e051678a7b2f7a7085b3dfe6","tid":1535673,"uid":260292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T12:33:56.000Z","msg":"由林奠2019因著陳同佳案硬推逃犯條例出現果刻<br />\n所謂神蹟已經出現左<br />\n抗爭最需要天時，地利，人和<br />\n<br />\n天時即國際局勢，中美質易戰，台灣大選前夕<br />\n2018，2020都唔會有咁好嘅「天時」<br />\n<br />\n「地利」唔洗多講，亞洲金融中心，最獨特嘅經濟特區<br />\n<br />\n到「人和」<br />\n因為陳同佳案而急著要推逃犯條例還潘家公道<br />\n可能你會話無陳同佳，政府都會有其他籍口推逃犯條例，但千千萬萬嘅籍口裡面，佢地搵左最on9嘅籍口去推逃犯條例，係人都知政府講大話，引發69大遊行之後嘅事唔洗多講<br />\n<br />\n我地嘅「人和」除左香港人之外已經linkup緊全世界反共反Chinazi<br />\n<br />\n天時地利人和我地都齊撚晒，黎明前係會最黑暗<br />\n我地流左好多血汗，損失左好多手足<br />\n但每次都令魔鬼更加露出原形<br />\n<br />\n就算唔信上帝都好<br />\n但我地已經活喺「天時地利人和」嘅奇蹟裡面<br />\n我地一定會贏，還返個公道俾每一個手足，我地一定要贏"},{"pid":"0d6cb0c8168f8a53879c0fde16207ea517bbd653","tid":1535673,"uid":167883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T12:34:15.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyixFQQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnyixFQQ.png&h=cc1f24a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月8日 (日) 2PM<br />\n香港人權與民主法案集會<br />\n美國駐港澳總領事館</strong></div><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"234d0a2417057d3078a0c1445540c905349a9847","tid":1535673,"uid":69753,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T12:35:36.000Z","msg":"有冇出現埋右?"},{"pid":"671b627a3ab45adcbc90a93bb41f9bbb3715ffe5","tid":1535673,"uid":263058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T12:36:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bbe4e5d6128f3a479de8499a01d485de227e056e","tid":1535673,"uid":34816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T12:41:27.000Z","msg":"907 入機場<br />\n908 美領見"},{"pid":"e39c11c313f8a1dfffa6dc2b172b127909aa2de2","tid":1535673,"uid":32022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T12:45:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WOZAG4S.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWOZAG4S.png&h=e5809465&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"704f9aaa251d84143e19badb62b225f784fc25c5","tid":1535673,"uid":39205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T12:48:30.000Z","msg":"[短期目標] 要求黨鐵交出831當晚CCTV<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1535686\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1535686</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"f32dfe361c9d5bfd1c0bfb2b4d0fe49f1ba38676","tid":1535673,"uid":266362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T12:55:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\">想大個仔獨立必睇</span></span></span></strong><br />\n［召喚攬炒巴] 星球級反擊！香港最後本錢 VS 赤獸<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1529054\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1529054</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n請幫推以